and how sometimes it is unruly

00:02:59.710 --> 00:03:02.810
and untamed and uncontrollable.

00:03:02.810 --> 00:03:05.660
And, I think we can apply
that to body sometimes,

00:03:05.660 --> 00:03:07.260
