00:03:07.260 --> 00:03:10.760
my body has felt unruly
and beyond my control.

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:14.760
And so, I think it's a
really appropriate phrase.

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:16.060
&gt;&gt; Linda Holmes: Yeah.

00:03:16.060 --> 00:03:20.170
I referred to this somewhat in
gest, but it has been my experience

00:03:20.170 --> 00:03:22.620
that since you wrote this book,

00:03:22.620 --> 00:03:27.970
